# ═══════════════════════════════════════════
# ❌ VALIDATION TESTS (Expected: 400)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### 38. Missing required fields (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Only Name"
}

###

### 39. Invalid email format (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "notanemail",
  "password": "pass"
}

###

### 40. Invalid expense category (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

{
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "INR",
  "category": "invalid_category",
  "description": "test",
  "date": "2025-03-15"
}

###

### 41. Negative amount (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

{
  "amount": -50,
  "currency": "INR",
  "category": "travel",
  "description": "test expense",
  "date": "2025-03-15"
}

###

### 42. Employee accessing admin route (expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

###
